n.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForegrounding%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20hit%20the%20campaign%20trail%20six%20months%20ago%20with%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMehngai%20rahat%3C%2Fem%3E%20camp%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20convey%20to%20the%20people%20the%20benefits%20they%20could%20accrue%20from%20the%20initiatives%20of%20the%20Gehlot%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%201%2C38%2C00%2C000%20families%20are%20linked%20to%20Mukhyamantri%20Chiranjeevi%20Swasthya%20Bima%20Yojana%20allowing%20them%20to%20get%20free%20health%20services%20at%20private%20hospitals.%20At%2072%2C%20Gehlot%20held%20four%20to%20five%20rallies%20in%20a%20day%20while%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20only%20seen%20eight%20days%20before%20polling%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20list%20of%20assembly%20segments%20where%20Gandhi%20campaigned%20and%20the%20electoral%20outcome%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaranagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20Taranagar%2C%20a%20hotly%20contested%20seat%20where%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rajendra%20Rathore%20gave%20a%20tough%20fight.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20campaigned%20for%20this%20seat%20on%20November%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBundi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20Bundi%20yielded%20success%20as%20Congress%20swept%20all%20three%20seats%3A%20Bundi%2C%20Keshoraipatan%2C%20and%20Hindoli.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20party%20won%20only%20one%20Hindoli%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDausa%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dausa%2C%20a%20region%20where%20Sachin%20Pilot%20has%20a%20strong%20influence%2C%20includes%20seats%20such%20as%20Bassi%2C%20Chaksu%2C%20Thanagazi%2C%20Bandikui%2C%20Mahuwa%2C%20Sikrai%2C%20Dausa%2C%20and%20Lalsot.%20The%20party%20lost%20most%20of%20the%20Dausa%20seats%20this%20time%2C%20possibly%20because%20of%20the%20Gurjar%20community%E2%80%99s%20anger%20against%20the%20party%20for%20not%20appointing%20its%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20width%3D%5C%22593%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3EConstituency%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3EWinners%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3EParty%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3EChaksu%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3ERamvatar%20Bairwa%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3EBJP%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3EBassi%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3ELaxman%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3ECongress%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3EBandikui%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3EBhagchand%20Tankda%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3EBJP%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3EThanagazi%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3EKanti%20Prasad%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3ECongress%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3EMahuwa%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3ERajendra%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3EBJP%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3ESikrai%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3EVikram%20Bansiwal%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3EBJP%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3EDausa%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3EMurari%20Lal%20Meena%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3ECongress%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%3ELalsot%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3ERambilas%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2297%5C%22%3EBJP%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Barmer%20Area%20Constituency%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20win%20only%20one%20seat%20in%202018%2C%20Congress%20secured%20one%20seat%20this%20time%2C%20with%20sitting%20MLA%20Harish%20Choudhary%20emerging%20victorious%20in%20Baytoo.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20addressed%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20this%20area.%20However%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20seats%20shifted%20from%20Congress%20to%20BJP%20or%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20continued%20his%20campaign%20in%20the%20Dholpur%20region%2C%20where%20the%20party%20had%20previously%20won%20six%20out%20of%20eight%20seats%20in%202018.%20This%20time%2C%20Congress%20secured%20five%20out%20of%20eight%20seats%2C%20while%20one%20went%20to%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20and%20two%20to%20BJP.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20change%20in%20political%20dynamics%20since%20the%20last%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20initially%20came%20out%20with%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKam%20Kiya%20Dil%20se%2C%20Gehlot%20Phir%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20later%20changed%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKam%20kiya%20dil%20se%2C%20Congress%20phir%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20as%20the%20party%20leadership%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20disappoint%20the%20Sachin%20Pilot%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20this%20time%20the%20party%20failed%20to%20influence%20Gurjar%20votes%20in%20the%20state.%20Gurjars%2C%20Jats%2C%20Rajputs%2C%20and%20Meenas%20play%20key%20roles%20in%20forming%20the%20government.%20Gurjars%E2%80%99s%20anger%20is%20palpable%20over%20not%20handing%20over%20the%20reins%20to%20Pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20holds%20influence%20over%20around%2030%20seats%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20Karauli%2C%20Tonk%2C%20Hindaun%2C%20and%20Dausa%20districts%20of%20eastern%20Rajasthan.%20Out%20of%20the%2031%20seats%20that%20the%20Congress%20lost%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20election%2C%2014%20come%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Frajasthan-assembly%2Frajasthan-assembly-election-results-gujjar-disenchantment-costs-the-congress-dearly%2Farticle67602067.ece%5C%22%3Eeastern%20part%20of%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Pilot%E2%80%99s%20community%2C%20the%20Gujjars%2C%20hold%20sway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-profile%20assembly%20seats%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmber%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Satish%20Poonia%2C%20a%20prominent%20Jat%20leader%20and%20former%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20state%2C%20lost%20to%20Prashanth%20Sharma%20by%20a%20margin%20of%209%2C092%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENathdwara%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20C.P.%20Joshi%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20speaker%2C%20faced%20defeat%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%20with%20a%20margin%20of%207504%20votes.%20Singh%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20royal%20family%20of%20Mewar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKota-North%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%2C%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20managed%20to%20win%20the%20Kota-North%20seat%20with%20a%20narrow%20margin%20of%202%2C000%20votes%20from%20Prahlad%20Gunjal.%20Interestingly%2C%20this%20marks%20the%20first%20time%20Dhariwal%20secured%20the%20seat%20while%20Congress%20didn%E2%80%99t%20win%20the%20state%2C%20as%20he%20typically%20loses%20his%20constituency%20when%20Congress%20loses%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECivil%20Lines%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pratap%20Singh%20Khachariyawas%2C%20another%20minister%20in%20the%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20lost%20his%20seat%20with%20a%20significant%20margin%20of%2028%2C329%20votes%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Gopal%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKaman%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Minister%20Zahida%20Khan%20also%20faced%20defeat%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Nauksham%20Choudhary.%20The%20people%20of%20Deeg%20had%20been%20demanding%20that%20Congress%20not%20give%20a%20ticket%20to%20Zahida%20Khan%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20killing%20of%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20in%20her%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20prominent%20figures%20such%20as%20Pramod%20Jain%2C%20B.D.%20Kalla%20(Bikaner%20West)%2C%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Jatav%20(Weir)%2C%20Mamta%20Bhupesh%20(Sikrai)%2C%20Parsadi%20Lal%20Meena%20(Lalsot)%2C%20Sukhram%20Vishnoi%20(Sanchore)%2C%20and%20Ramlal%20Jat%20(Mandal)%20also%20lost%20their%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20seven-time%20BJP%20MLA%20and%20a%20significant%20figure%20in%20Rajasthan%20politics%2C%20Rajendra%20Rathore%2C%20was%20defeated%20from%20Taranagar%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2010%2C345%20votes%20to%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Narendra%20Budania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Taranagar%20was%20the%20only%20place%20where%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20campaigned%20for%20Congress%20on%20November%2016%2C%20just%20eight%20days%20before%20the%20voting%20on%20November%2025%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20time%20of%20ticket%20distribution%2C%20the%20senior%20leadership%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20happy%20with%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20and%20influence%20in%20ticket%20distribution%2C%20which%20later%20resulted%20in%20significant%20losses%20for%20the%20party.%20Despite%20this%2C%20candidates%20like%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20from%20Kota-North%20managed%20to%20secure%20a%20place%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%2C%20even%20though%20senior%20leadership%20had%20questioned%20and%20alleged%20him%20as%20a%20corrupt%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20was%20largely%20absent%20from%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Though%20he%20referred%20to%20Rajasthan%20government%20welfare%20schemes%20during%20his%20campaign%20in%20other%20states%2C%20he%20did%20not%20hold%20any%20roadshow.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701776115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22112200%2FF84a12kXkAAI7Ua.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgehlot-pilot-rivalry-congress-drubbing-rajasthan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%