A%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%2C%20safeguards%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20for%20the%20union%20territory%20and%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20any%20assurance%20on%20fulfilling%20these%20demands%2C%20but%20told%20the%20leadership%20of%20Ladakh%20that%20talks%20will%20continue%20to%20address%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20told%20the%20delegation%20that%20the%20government%20will%20look%20at%20options%20on%20how%20to%20address%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Chering%20Dorjay%2C%20former%20minister%20and%20member%20of%20Apex%20Body%20Leh%2C%20said%20they%20raised%20the%20four%20-point%20agenda%20during%20the%20meeting.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20minister%20listened%20to%20our%20demands%2C%20but%20neither%20rejected%20them%20nor%20accepted%20them.%20He%20told%20us%20that%20they%20will%20hold%20another%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20these%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20statehood%20demand%2C%20Dorjay%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20neither%20said%20yes%20nor%20no.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProminent%20political%20and%20social%20activist%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(KDA)%20Sajjad%20Kargili%20said%20that%20they%20told%20the%20Centre%20that%20these%20four%20demands%20should%20be%20met%20to%20fulfil%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20told%20that%20the%20committee%20will%20meet%20again%20after%20the%20ongoing%20winter%20session%20is%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CCold%E2%80%9D%20on%20statehood%20demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20could%20indicate%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20cold%20attitude%20towards%20the%20demand%20for%20statehood%2C%20an%20official%20handout%20released%20after%20the%20talks%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20raised%20by%20the%20Ladakhi%20delegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ABL%20and%20KDA%20members%20submitted%20various%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20protection%20of%20rights%20of%20Ladakh%20residents%2C%20fast%20track%20recruitment%20processes%2C%20strengthening%20of%20LAHDCs%2C%20Greater%20participation%20in%20the%20decision%20making%20etc.%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20official%20handout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20New%20Delhi%20would%20continue%20talks%20with%20the%20ABL%20and%20KDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShri%20Rai%20said%20that%20the%20Government%20would%20continue%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20ABL%20and%20KDA%20and%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20for%20holistic%20and%20sustainable%20development%20of%20the%20UT%20of%20Ladakh%20on%20regular%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Ladakh%2C%20Jamyang%20Tsering%20Namgayal%2C%20has%20pushed%20for%20constitutional%20safeguards%20beyond%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20for%20safeguarding%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20identity%20and%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20firmly%20advocate%20the%20necessity%20for%20constitutional%20safeguards%20exceeding%20the%20provisions%20laid%20down%20in%20the%206th%20schedule%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20specifically%20tailored%20to%20safeguard%20the%20interests%20and%20aspirations%20of%20tribal%20people%20of%20Ladakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20MP%E2%80%99s%20letter%20to%20the%20MoS%20home%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20the%20autonomous%20district%20councils%20have%20specific%20legislative%2C%20executive%2C%20judicial%20and%20f