t%3BBut%20it%20feels%20wrong%20leaving%20them!!%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20server%2C%20don't%20do%20it%20if%20u%20can't%20stack%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20comment%20reads.%20%26quot%3BBut%20thank%20you%20to%20those%20who%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20commenters%20seemed%20to%20agree%20there%20was%20a%20correct%20way%20to%20help%20out%20the%20staff%2C%20and%20that%20was%20not%20to%20stuff%20napkins%20into%20any%20cups%20or%20sauce%20left%20on%20the%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20wanna%20fish%20ur%20utensils%20or%20napkins%20out%20of%20food%20or%20any%20type%20of%20liquid%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20stuffing%20napkins%20in%20bowls%20or%20drinks%20that%20gets%20annoying%2C%20because%20then%20I%20have%20to%20fish%20them%20out%20and%20they're%20all%20soggy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%20%26quot%3BLove%20the%20plate%20stacking%20though.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20servers%20said%20they%20usually%20appreciated%20guests%20stacking%20the%20plates%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20restaurant%20is%20busy%2C%20and%20if%20they%20make%20one%20%26quot%3Btrash%20plate%26quot%3B%20with%20all%20the%20leftovers%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20better%20than%20leaving%20a%20huge%20mess!%26quot%3B%20one%20server%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20make%20sure%20the%20silverware%20isn't%20gonna%20fall%20off%20the%20plate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20all%20I%20care%20about%20lol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20tip%20to%20note%20was%20not%20to%20slack%20plates%20on%20top%20of%20silverware%2C%20several%20servers%20pointed%20out%2C%20because%20it%20makes%20the%20tower%20unsteady.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20find%20out%20until%20you%20almost%20drop%206%20plates%20on%20grandma%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fservers-ignite-debate-about-stacking-plates-at-end-of-meal-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701773054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656ef6767a3c8094d5d98d1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fservers-ignite-debate-about-stacking-plates-at-end-of-meal-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jorj%20Fuchs%20and%20her%20friend%2C%20who%20both%20work%20in%20food%20service%2C%20stacked%20their%20plates%20at%20the%20end%20of%20their%20meal%2C%20saying%20they%20know%20fellow%20servers%20%26quot%3Bhate%20when%20we%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fservers-ignite-debate-about-stacking-plates-at-end-of-meal-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20regulators%20inspect%20Dr%20Reddy's%2C%20other%20Indian%20pharma%20majors%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701772776000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-05%2F22%2Ffull%2F1653236018-1419.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fus-regulators-inspect-dr-reddy-s-other-indian-pharma-majors-report-123120500649_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rivals%20Sun%20Pharma's%20Dadra%20facility%20and%20Torrent%20Pharmaceuticals%20Ltd's%20oncology%20unit%20are%20also%20undergoing%20FDA%20inspections%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fus-regulators-inspect-dr-reddy-s-other-indian-pharma-majors-report-123120500649_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fus-regulators-inspect-dr-reddy-s-other-indian-pharma-majors-report-123120500649_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fus-regulators-inspect-dr-reddy-s-other-indian-pharma-majors-report-123120500649_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20A%20Mandate%20for%20Mehnat%20-%20By%20Vinay%20Sahasrabuddhe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20election%20verdict%20has%20distinct%20messages%20and%20important%20lessons%2C%20if%20one%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20them.%20When%20one%20deciphers%20the%20recent%20mandate%20secured%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20at%20least%20four%20important%20points%20emerge.%20First%2C%20good%20governance%20and%20women's%20empowerment%20pays%3B%20second%2C%20the%20days%20of%20banking%20on%20vote%20banks%20are%20over%3B%20third%2C%20corruption%20has%20a%20cost%3B%20and%20finally%2C%20organisational%20strength%20helps%20break%20new%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20splendid%20success%20has%20astonished%20many%2C%20including%20a%20section%20of%20its%20own%20cadres.%20While%20Rajasthan%20was%20no%20surprise%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20made%20many%20realise%20that%20although%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20fly%20between%20parties%2C%20they%20stick%20only%20when%20coming%20from%20a%20clean%20and%20credible%20leader.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP's%20success%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20just%20unparalleled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20many%20had%20gone%20by%20conventional%20presumptions.%20They%20talked%20about%20voter%20fatigue%2C%20anti-incumbency%2C%20generational%20change%20and%20limitations%20of%20the%20narrative%20around%20development.%20Hence%2C%20it%20was%20not%20surprising%20that%20many%20political%20pundits%20were%20skeptical%20about%20the%20BJP's%20chances%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20A%20deeper%20analysis%20of%20the%20results%20reveals%20one%20powerful%20message%20-%20people%20support%20those%20who%20deliver%20good%20governance%20and%20women's%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20the%20solid%20foundation%20of%20the%20party%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20built%20historically%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Kushabhau%20Thackrey%20and%20others%2C%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20translating%20the%20goodwill%20into%20voter%20mobilisation.%20Notably%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20more%20than%20most%20states%2C%20has%20a%20significant%20chunk%20of%20cadre%20with%20an%20unshakeable%20commitment%20to%20ideology%20and%20organization%2C%20which%20makes%20a%20huge%20difference.%20Also%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20voters%20here%20have%20not%20just%20seen%20but%20experienced%20empowerment%2C%20as%20a%20cascading%20effect%20of%20development.%20Take%20the%20example%20of%20Mohapura%20dam%20in%20Rajgadh%20district.%20This%20irrigation%20project%20is%20unique%20as%20it%20irrigates%20with%20pressure%2C%20allowing%20only%20the%20sprinkler%20system-based%20piping%20network%20and%20prohibiting%20open%20canals.%20Adequate%20water%20supply%20to%201%20lakh%2035%20hectares%20of%20land%20has%20motivated%20farmers%20to%20cultivate%20their%20land%20through%20the%20year%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20has%20stopped%20the%20seasonal%20migration%20of%20farm%20labourers.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20for%20many%20other%20projects.%20Roads%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20of%20far%20better%20quality%20than%20many%20states.%20Indore%20retaining%20the%20cleanest%20city%20tag%20for%20six%20consecutive%20years%20is%20also%20no%20small%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20say%20the%20aspirational%20district%2Fblock%20development%20programme%20of%20the%20government%20has%20truly%20transformed%20lives%20in%20districts%20that%20were%20once%20most%20backward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20won%20two%20of%2081%20seats%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20compared%20to%2023%20earlier.%20The%20BJP's%20performance%20in%20tribal%20seats%20also%20tells%20us%20the%20same%20story.%20However%2C%20the%20most%20clinching%20evidence%20of%20%26quot%3Bexperiential%20empowerment%26quot%3B%20comes%20through%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20scheme.%20An%20assured%20amount%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts%20operated%20by%20them%20has%20enhanced%20the%20self-esteem%20of%20women.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20no%20longer%20dependent%20on%20their%20husbands.%20This%20sense%20of%20becoming%20%3Cem%3Eatmanirbhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(self-reliant)%20had%20an%20electrifying%20impact%20on%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan's%20%26quot%3Bsisters%26quot%3B%20who%20stood%20by%20him%20like%20a%20rock.%20Finally%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20ability%20to%20strike%20an%20emotional%20connect%20with%20the%20voters%20tilted%20the%20scales%20completely%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20although%20the%20BJP's%20success%20was%20less%20surprising%2C%20an%20inert%20and%20helpless%20Congress%20leadership%20effectively%20demoralised%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20his%20faction%2C%20already%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20BJP's%20convincingly%20mounted%20attack%20on%20his%20vote-bank%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20in%20Rajasthan%20but%20elsewhere%20too%2C%20issues%20like%20Love%20Jihad%20are%20real.%20Except%20the%20BJP%2C%20no%20other%20political%20party%20had%20the%20courage%20to%20raise%20issues%20that%20resonate%20with%20the%20fear%20lurking%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20scores%20of%20Indians.%20Remember%2C%20most%20opposition%20parties%20have%20always%20chosen%20to%20look%20the%20other%20way%20when%20the%20BJP%20raised%20such%20issues.%20Unsurprisingly%2C%20its%20consistent%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress's%20vote%20bank%20politics%20motivated%20voters%20to%20support%20the%20BJP.%20Add%20to%20this%20the%20razor-sharp%20criticism%20by%20PM%20Modi%20over%20a%20secretive%20red%20diary%20of%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20and%20you%20have%20an%20already%20split%20house%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20Congress%20collapse%20like%20a%20pack%20of%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victory%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20was%20perhaps%20most%20remarkable%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Here%20again%2C%20cursing%20Mahadeva%20did%20cost%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20very%20heavily.%20Also%2C%20when%20PM%20Modi%20attacks%20a%20rival%20party%20leader%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20corruption%2C%20it%20works%20wonders.%20In%20most%20tribal%20areas%2C%20protecting%20identity%20and%20culture%20has%20always%20remained%20an%20issue.%20The%20BJP's%20track%20record%20of%20voicing%20these%20concerns%20and%20taking%20credible%20measures%20to%20prevent%20attacks%20on%20their%20identity%20resonates%20with%20the%20tribals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%20too%2C%20the%20BJP%20reaching%20a%20voter%20base%20of%20almost%2014%25%20should%20ring%20a%20warning%20bell%20for%20regional%20parties%20whose%20only%20strength%20is%20in%20their%20plank%20based%20on%20regionalism.%20Those%20who%20portray%20the%20BJP's%20failure%20in%20this%20southern%20state%20as%20an%20indication%20of%20a%20North-South%20divide%20often%20forget%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20already%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20of%20Puducherry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20making%20a%20headway%20in%20Mizoram%20while%20winning%20two%20seats%20tells%20us%20about%20the%20resoluteness%20with%20which%20party%20cadres%20work%20for%20years%20in%20a%20particular%20area.%20The%20party%20has%20always%20believed%20that%20while%20creating%20a%20politically%20favourable%20climate%20or%20a%20wave%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20party%20is%20important%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20organisation%20cannot%20be%20undermined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20these%20points%2C%20what%20finally%20helped%20the%20BJP%20is%20the%20towering%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Modi.%20Remember%2C%20it%20is%20not%20magic.%20It%20is%20his%20%3Cem%3Emehnat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20ability%20to%20sweat%20it%20out%3B%20working%20almost%20about%2018%20hours%20every%20single%20day.%20His%20strong%20political%20will%2C%20his%20creativity%20in%20weaving%20campaign%20themes%2C%20also%20manifested%20in%20his%20carefully%20curated%20speeches%2C%20his%20consistent%20'ear-to-the-ground'%2C%20and%20the%20courage%20of%20conviction%20in%20his%20sharp%20attacks%20on%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20counts%20of%20dynasty%20politics%2C%20corruption%20and%20mis-governance%20provide%20him%20an%20eternal%20plank.%20One%20must%20remember%20that%20an%20attack%20from%20other%20political%20leaders%20and%20one%20from%20PM%20Modi%20are%20substantially%2C%20qualitatively%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20things%20put%20together%2C%20it%20is%20a%20mandate%20for%20%3Cem%3Emehnat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVinay%20Sahasrabuddhe%20is%20former%20MP%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20columnist%2C%20besides%20being%20President%20of%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Cultural%20Relations%20(ICCR)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701772740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F9i1eseso_modi-ani_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-mandate-for-mehnat-by-vinay-sahasrabuddhe-4634754%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20election%20verdict%20has%20distinct%20messages%20and%20important%20lessons%2C%20if%20one%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20them.%20When%20one%20deciphers%20the%20recent%20mandate%20secured%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20at%20least%204%20important%20points%20emerge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-mandate-for-mehnat-by-vinay-sahasrabuddhe-4634754%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-mandate-for-mehnat-by-vinay-sahasrabuddhe-4634754%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-mandate-for-mehnat-by-vinay-sahasrabuddhe-4634754%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Pakistan's%20Tour%20Goes%20From%20Bad%20To%20Worse%20As