rth%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F09%2F10%2Fopinion%2Fsway-kara-swisher-trailer.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengulfed%20by%20its%20expanding%20sun%3C%2Fa%3E%20(something%20that%20won't%20happen%20for%20at%20least%205%20billion%20years).%20But%20lately%20the%20apocalypse%20that's%20most%20preoccupied%20Musk%20is%20the%20one%20where%20artificial%20intelligence%20becomes%20powerful%20enough%20to%20take%20over%20the%20world%20and%20kill%20all%20humans.%20That%20led%20him%20to%20start%20Neuralink%2C%20a%20brain-computer-interface%20company%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fneuralink-is-impressive-tech-wrapped-in-musk-hype%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletting%20humans%20intermingle%20with%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-thinks-openai-sam-altman-made-dangerous-ai-discovery-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecofound%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20in%20a%20twist%20only%20ChatGPT%20could%20love%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-openai-board-member-were-not-slowing-openai-down-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epivoted%20to%20creating%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20powerful%20enough%20to%20take%20over%20the%20world%20and%20kill%20all%20humans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20apocalyptic%20mindset%20dovetails%20conveniently%20with%20Musk's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-mars-longtermism-baby-sea-turtles-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20of%20longtermism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20ideology%20that%20says%20you're%20allowed%20to%20do%20pretty%20much%20anything%20you%20want%20right%20now%20as%20long%20as%20it%20saves%20trillions%20of%20lives%20in%20the%20distant%20future.%20Hence%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20the%20ultimate%20status%20symbol%20for%20the%20end%20times.%20If%20you're%20looking%20to%20justify%20an%20apocalyptic%20world%20in%20which%20you%20tool%20around%20in%20a%20%2461%2C000%20pickup%20truck%20while%20everyone%20else%20eats%20their%20young%2C%20then%20this%20is%20the%20vehicle%20for%20you.%20Sure%2C%20all%20those%20losers%20crammed%20into%20a%20265th-floor%20walkup%20in%20Megacity%20One%20will%20be%20jealous%20as%20you%20cruise%20past%20them%20in%20your%20sweet%2C%20sweet%20ride.%20But%20all%20they're%20doing%20is%20surviving.%20Your%20job%20%E2%80%94%20your%20mission%2C%20really%20%E2%80%94%20is%20to%20ensure%20the%20continuation%20of%20human%20civilization.%20And%20to%20do%20that%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20need%20something%20with%20armored%20glass%2C%20a%202%2C500-pound%20payload%2C%20and%20an%20interior%20%26quot%3Bas%20quiet%20as%20outer%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20if%20you%20really%20want%20something%20apocalyptic%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20has%20killed%20or%20maimed%20millions%2C%20that%20remade%20the%20landscape%20into%20something%20inhuman%20and%20bleak%2C%20that%20grew%20out%20of%20a%20devilish%20bargain%20promising%20freedom%20and%20delivering%20fear%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20we%20already%20have%20that.%20It's%20trucks!%20Barely%20two%20weeks%20before%20the%20Cybertruck%20launch%2C%20the%20Insurance%20Institute%20for%20Highway%20Safety%20published%20new%20data%20confirming%20what%20car%20researchers%20have%20been%20saying%20for%20years.%20Trucks%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iihs.org%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2Fvehicles-with-higher-more-vertical-front-ends-pose-greater-risk-to-pedestrians%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E45%25%20more%20likely%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20kill%20a%20person%20they%20hit%20than%20smaller%20vehicles.%20Places%20with%20more%20trucks%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1016%2Fj.ecotra.2021.100219%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20pedestrian%20deaths%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20do%20cities%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com%2Fretrieve%2Fpii%2FS2542519619302633%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20roads%20and%20less%20public%20transit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20nation's%20pedestrian%20death%20toll%20has%20soared%20by%2080%25%20since%202009%2C%20thanks%20in%20large%20part%20to%20ever%20rising%20truck%20sizes%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esales.%20That's%2020%20dead%20people%20%3Cem%3Eevery%20day%3C%2Fem%3E.%20And%20that's%20not%20counting%20all%20the%20air%20pollution%20and%20deforestation%20and%20global%20warming%20that%20trucks%20are%20helping%20to%20fuel.%20The%20truckpocalypse%20is%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%2020th%20century%2C%20when%20cars%20first%20came%20within%20financial%20reach%20of%20average%20Americans%2C%20the%20sales%20pitch%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1177%2F0263276404046066%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreedom%20of%20movement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20with%20trucks%2C%20the%20marketing%20has%20changed.%20Giant%20trucks%20represent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdx.doi.org%2F10.1016%2Fj.eist.2015.02.001%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esecurity%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20cocooned%20safety%20of%20the%20passengers%20against%20an%20increasingly%20hostile%20world.%20The%20Cybertruck%20takes%20this%20idea%20to%20its%20logical%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theonion.com%2Fconscientious-suv-shopper-just-wants-something-that-wil-1844930331%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elolsob%20hilarious%20extreme%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20doesn't%20just%20park%20inside%20the%20armor%20dome%3B%20it%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20armor%20dome.%20And%20to%20make%20that%20sales%20pitch%20stick%2C%20the%20people%20hawking%20the%20trucks%20have%20to%20make%20us%20believe%20that%20the%20world%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20getting%20increasingly%20hostile.%20Make%20sure%20everyone%20can%20buy%20a%20gun%2C%20then%20sell%20everyone%20a%20bulletproof%20car.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWriters%20from