%20new%20experiences%2C%20build%20skills%20and%20advance%20their%20personal%20development%20through%20short-term%20assignments%20and%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20many%20times%20in%20a%20different%20function%2C%20business%20unit%20or%20geography%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCoca-Cola%20also%20works%20closely%20with%20our%20bottling%20partners%20to%20invest%20in%20trade%20schools%20and%20on-the-job%20training%20in%20manufacturing%20plants%20and%20distribution%20centers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20earners%20at%20Coca-Cola%20are%20nearly%20four%20times%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20been%20hired%20internally%20versus%20its%20rival%20PepsiCo%2C%20the%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20companies%20that%20made%20the%20top%20five%20were%20J.M.%20Smucker%2C%20W.W.%20Grainger%2C%20PNC%20Financial%20Services%20Group%2C%20and%20Service%20Now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20came%20in%20at%20six%20and%20was%20highly%20rated%20on%20racial%20and%20gender%20parity%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20pay.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20rated%20a%20score%20of%20one%20for%20its%20hiring%20practices%2C%20which%20looks%20at%20whether%20the%20company%20is%20good%20at%20hiring%20inexperienced%20people%20or%20those%20without%20college%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20brutal%20layoffs%20and%20cost-cutting%20measures%2C%20Meta%20dropped%20off%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-apple-no-longer-best-places-tech-companies-work-glassdoor-2023-1%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20Glassdoor's%20list%20of%20the%20best%20places%20to%20work%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20in%202023.%20It%20previously%20made%20the%20list%20every%20year%20since%202011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20tech%20firms%20including%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Salesforce%20also%20made%20the%20AOI%20top%20100%20list%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco%20was%20the%20top%20retailer%20on%20the%20list%20and%20came%20in%20at%2