20need%20to%20be%20activated%2C%20and%20have%20to%20take%20cognizance%20of%20material%20information%20that%20is%20brought%20to%20their%20knowledge%2C%20including%20non-public%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20engaging%20and%20being%20receptive%20to%20stakeholders%2C%20the%20SRCs%20can%20adopt%20a%20forward-looking%20approach.%20To%20operate%20successfully%2C%20the%20SRCs%20would%20need%20to%20be%20more%20proactive%20and%20engage%20with%20employee%20representatives%2C%20which%20is%20difficult%20in%20many%20private%20sector%20banks%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20staff%20unions%20and%20officer%20associations.%20Seeking%20advice%20from%20proxy%20advisory%20firms%20and%20even%20analysts%20covering%20the%20concerned%20companies%20may%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rejection%20of%20the%20renewal%20of%20the%20term%20of%20an%20independent%20director%20by%20IndusInd%20Bank%20shareholders%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20supported%20by%20the%20founder%20and%20the%20board%2C%20is%20a%20major%20embarrassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20renewal%20complied%20with%20regulatory%20norms%2C%20the%20rejection%20highlights%20the%20board%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20concern%20for%20current%20governance%20norms%2C%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20SRC%20in%20briefing%20the%20board%20regarding%20the%20concerns%20of%20proxy%20advisory%20firms.%20Company%20boards%20have%20an%20organisational%20structure%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20SRC%2C%20to%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20but%20this%20structure%20needs%20to%20be%20activated%20in%20order%20to%20improve%20governance%20in%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHemindra%20Hazari%20is%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20registered%20independent%20research%20analyst%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDISCLOSURE%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-attr%3D%5C%22not-done%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%2C%20Hemindra%20Hazari%2C%20am%20a%20Securities%20and%20