eports%20claimed%20that%20he%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20Virat%20Kohli's%20removal.%20However%2C%20he%20has%20said%20now%20that%20he%20had%20no%20role%20to%20play%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20remove%20Virat%20from%20captaincy.%20I%20have%20said%20this%20several%20times.%20He%20(Kohli)%20was%20not%20interested%20to%20lead%20in%20T20Is.%20So%2C%20after%20he%20made%20that%20decision%2C%20I%20told%20him%2C%20if%20you're%20not%20interested%20to%20lead%20in%20T20Is%2C%20it's%20better%20if%20you%20step%20down%20from%20entire%20white-ball%20cricket%20formats.%20Let%20there%20be%20a%20white-ball%20captain%20and%20a%20red-ball%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DptrJ_6HrmWI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDadagiri%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20pushed%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20bit%20to%20take%20up%20the%20captaincy%20role%20because%20he%20wasn't%20interested%20to%20lead%20in%20all%20three%20formats%20of%20the%20game.%20So%2C%20maybe%20I%20have%20a%20bit%20of%20contribution%20in%20that%20but%20no%20matter%20who%20is%20administrating%2C%20it's%20the%20players%20who%20perform%20well%20on%20the%20field.%20No%20body%20from%20outside%20can%20contribute%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20President%20of%20BCCI%20to%20work%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20this%20is%20a%20small%20part%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Kohli's%20exit%20as%20India's%20captain%20across%20three%20formats%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20given%20the%20team's%20baton%20in%20T20Is%2C%20ODIs%20as%20well%20as%20Tests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%207%20years%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20toil%20and%20relentless%20perseverance%20everyday%20to%20take%20the%20team%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20I%20have%20done%20the%20job%20with%20absolute%20honesty%20and%20left%20nothing%20out%20there.%20Every%20thing%20has%20to%20come%20to%20a%20halt%20at%20some%20stage%20and%20for%20me%20as%20Test%20captain%20of%20India%2C%20it's%20now.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20ups%20and%20also%20some%20downs%20along%20the%20journey%2C%20but%20never%20has%20there%20been%20a%20lack%20of%20effort%20or%20lack%20of%20belief.%20I%20have%20always%20believed%20in%20giving%20my%20120%20per%20cent%20in%20everything%20I%20do%2C%20and%20if%20I%20can't%20do%20that%2C%20I%20know%20its%20not%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%20I%20have%20absolute%20clarity%20in%20my%20heart%20and%20I%20cannot%20be%20dishonest%20to%20my%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20KOhli%20had%20said%20in%20his%20statement%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20BCCI%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20lead%20my%20country%20for%20such%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20to%20all%20the%20teammates%20who%20bought%20into%20the%20vision%20I%20had%20for%20the%20team%20from%20day%20one%20and%20never%20gave%20up%20in%20any%20situation.%20You%20guys%20have%20made%20this%20journey%20so%20memorable%20and%20beautiful.%20To%20Ravi%20bhai%20and%20the%20support%20group%20who%20were%20the%20engine%20behind%20this%20vehicle%20that%20moved%20us%20upwards%20in%20Test%20cricket%20consistently%2C%20you%20all%20have%20played%20a%20massive%20role%20in%20bringing%20this%20vision%20to%20life.%20Lastly%2C%20a%20big%20thank%20you%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20believed%20in%20me%20as%20a%20captain%20and%20found%20me%20to%20be%20an%20able%20individual%20who%20could%20take%20Indian%20Cricket%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701770220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%