a.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frashtriya-rajput-karni-sena-chief-sukhdev-singh-gogamedi-shot-dead-in-jaipur%2Farticleshow%2F105753284.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rashtriya%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%20chief%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%20shot%20dead%20in%20Jaipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701769704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105756475%2Cimgsize-30940.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fjaipur%2Frashtriya-rajput-karni-sena-national-president-sukhdev-singh-gogamedi-shot-dead-in-jaipur%2Farticleshow%2F105753343.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20of%20Right-wing%20group%20Shri%20Rashtriya%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%2C%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%2C%20was%20shjot%20dead%20by%20unidentified%20assailants%20in%20Rajasthan's%20capital%20Jaipur%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20Blog%3A%20Arjuna%20The%20Elephant%20Is%20Dead.%20I%20Hope%20He%20Is%20At%20Peace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArjuna%20is%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20news%20of%20the%20death%20of%20this%20majestic%20elephant%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20sorrow.%20Over%20several%20years%2C%20I%20had%20an%20annual%20rendezvous%20with%20the%20magnificent%20creature%20at%20the%20Ambavilas%20Palace%20in%20Mysuru%2C%20Karnataka%20-%20as%20he%20got%20ready%20to%20play%20his%20star%20role%20in%20the%20famous%20Vijayadashami%20procession.%20We%20would%20cover%20the%20procession%20live%20every%20year%20for%20TV%20as%20part%20of%20all-India%20festival%20coverage%20on%20NDTV.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20arrived%20at%20the%20palace%20grounds%2C%20I%20would%20walk%20down%20to%20Arjuna's%20enclosure%20to%20admire%20him%20and%20hope%20he%20was%20coping%20with%20the%20inevitable%20stress%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20learnt%20of%20the%20manner%20of%20his%20death%2C%20the%20sorrow%20intensified.%20I%20had%20first%20thought%20he%20had%20died%20of%20old%20age%20-%20he%20was%2063%20and%20had%20been%20retired%20from%20carrying%20the%20750%20kg%20golden%20Howrah%20and%20the%20idol%20of%20Goddess%20Chamundeshwari%20during%20the%20Dasara%20procession.%20However%2C%20it%20wasn't%20a%20peaceful%20death%20for%20Arjuna%20in%20his%20forest%20home%20in%20Karnataka's%20Nagarahole%20forest.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20a%20Karnataka%20Forest%20Department%20operation%20to%20tackle%20a%20wild%20elephant%20in%20Sakaleshpur%20-%20and%20was%20killed%20by%20that%20elephant%20in%20a%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20pictures%20of%20grieving%20people%20sobbing%20on%20the%20injured%20body%20of%20the%20elephant.%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20posted%20on%20X%20his%20sorrow%20at%20the%20news.%20Thousands%20of%20people%20have%20seen%20Arjuna%20-%20and%20his%20death%20has%20affected%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMysuru's%20royal%20Dasara%20tradition%20goes%20back%20centuries.%20The%20festival%20is%20Karnataka's%20nada%20habba%2C%20the%20state%20festival.%20The%20Vijayadashami%20procession%20starts%20at%20the%20Mysuru%20palace%20and%20winds%20its%20way%20through%20the%20city.%20The%20highlight%20for%20thousands%20who%20watch%20the%20procession%20is%20the%20jumbo%20savari%20-%20the%20procession%20of%20beautifully%20decorated%20elephants.%20The%20'chief'%20elephant%20was%20given%20the%20task%20of%20carrying%20the%20weighty%20golden%20howdah.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Mysore%20Maharaja%20would%20sit%20in%20the%20howdah.%20Later%2C%20the%20howdah%20carried%20the%20idol%20of%20the%20goddess%20Chamundeshwari.%20The%20story%20around%20the%20Mysuru%20Dasara%20is%20that%20Chamundeshwari%20killed%20the%20demon%20Mahishasura%20-%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20name%20Mysuru.%20Mahishasura%20rode%20an%20enormous%20buffalo%2C%20so%20goes%20the%20story%2C%20and%20the%20Chamundi%20hill%20overlooking%20the%20city%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20body%20of%20that%20buffalo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Farjuna-elephant-ndtv_650x400_71506708096.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20of%20the%20ambari%20elephant%20-%20the%20elephant%20to%20carry%20the%20howdah%20-%20had%20to%20be%20a%20careful%20one.%20Arjuna%20was%20a%20risky%20choice%20for%20this%20role.%20He%20had%20been%20violent%20in%20the%20past.%20But%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20procession%2C%20he%20always%20came%20through%2C%20as%20he%20had%20been%20trained%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elephants%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Dasara%20procession%20spend%20most%20of%20the%20year%20in%20a%20forest%20camp.%20They%20are%20brought%20in%20from%20their%20forest%20home%20in%20Nagarahole%20several%20weeks%20before%20the%20procession%20-%20to%20acclimatise%20them%20to%20city%20noise%20and%20the%20hard%20roads.%20Many%20voice%20concern%20about%20what%20the%20elephants%20have%20to%20go%20through%20during%20it%20all.%20The%20sheer%20weight%20of%20the%20750kg%20golden%20howdah%20cannot%20be%20easy%20for%20the%20ambari%20elephants%2C%20however%20strong%20they%20are.%20Add%20to%20that%2C%20the%20crowds%2C%20the%20noise%2C%20the%20drumming...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20I%20would%20look%20into%20Arjuna's%20eyes%20and%20wonder%20what%20he%20was%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjuna%20was%20captured%20as%20a%20young%20eight-year-old%20from%20the%20forests%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats.%20He%20was%20trained.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2052%2C%20in%20the%20year%202012%2C%20he%20was%20chosen%20to%20be%20the%20ambari%20elephant%20despite%20worry%20over%20his%20temperament.%20He%20made%20it%20though%2C%20from%202012%20to%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%20to%20make%20his%20annual%20appearances%20at%20the%20Mysuru%20Dasara%20celebrations%2C%20and%20even%20when%20he%20was%20relieved%20of%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20howdah%20after%20he%20turned%2060%2C%20he%20was%20still%20part%20of%20the%20procession.%20This%20year%20too%2C%20during%20Vijayadashami%20in%202023%2C%20the%20veteran%20made%20his%20way%20from%20the%20forests%20to%20stay%20for%20weeks%20in%20the%20palace%20grounds%20and%20walk%20through%20the%20streets%20of%20Mysuru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20Arjuna%20once%20in%20his%20Nagarahole%20home%20too%2C%20during%20a%20shoot%20for%20NDTV's%20tiger%20campaign.%20He%20did%20have%20a%20chain%20around%20his%20leg%20-%20a%20'working'%20elephant%20can%20never%20be%20said%20to%20be%20totally%20free.%20But%20it%20was%20far%20more%20soothing%20to%20see%20the%20tall%2C%20dark%20and%20handsome%20Arjuna%20in%20the%20forest%20than%20in%20the%20urban%20settings%20where%20we%20usually%20met.%20I%20was%20allowed%20to%20feed%20him%20a%20ragi%20ball%20as%20he%20towered%20over%20me%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20a%20wooden%20barricade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20were%20you%20thinking%2C%20Arjuna%3F%20When%20you%20were%20taken%20into%20captivity%20as%20a%20young%20elephant.%20During%20your%20training.%20During%20the%20long%20years%20of%20Dasara%20service%20walking%20as%20part%20of%20a%20noisy%20procession.%20When%20you%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20you%20are%20at%20peace%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701769620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Farjuna-elephant-ndtv_650x400_71506708096.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Farjuna-the-elephant-is-dead-4635380%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arjuna%20is%20dead.%20When%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20news%20of%20the%20death%20of%20this%20majestic%20elephant%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sense%20o