%3E%20at%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20London%20during%20a%20protest%20by%20pro-Khalistan%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20investigation%20has%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20West%20Midlands%20police%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20claim%20that%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20sudden%20death%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthorough%20review%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20foul%20play%20suspected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhand%20died%20on%20June%2015%2C%20four%20days%20after%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Birmingham%2C%20UK.%20He%20was%20recently%20diagnosed%20with%20acute%20myeloid%20leukaemia%2C%20an%20aggressive%20blood%20cancer.%20His%20associates%20suspected%20foul%20play%20%E2%80%93%20claiming%20he%20was%20poisoned%20%E2%80%93%20but%20British%20officials%20did%20not%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereports%20that%20the%20West%20Midlands%20force%20%E2%80%9Cappeared%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20its%20original%20statement%20to%20the%20press%2C%20when%20it%20said%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20%E2%80%98thoroughly%E2%80%99%20investigated%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20police%20say%20they%20are%20still%20%E2%80%9Csatisfied%20that%20there%20are%20no%20suspicious%20circumstances%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhanda%E2%80%99s%20friends%2C%20fellow%20Sikh%20activists%20and%20family%20members%20told%20the%20UK%20newspaper%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinsistence%20by%20British%20authorities%20that%20a%20deeper%20investigation%20is%20not%20warranted%20fails%20to%20take%20into%20account%20damning%20details%20that%20have%20emerged%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20global%20campaign%20of%20transnational%20repression%20aimed%20at%20Sikh%20separatists%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20is%20facing%20allegations%20that%20its%20agents%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%3Einvolved%20in%20the%20killing%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20in%20Vancouver%20just%20days%20after%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20while%20a%20plot%20allegedly%20directed%20by%20an%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3Eidentified%20Indian%20government%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20to%20kill%20an%20American%20Sikh%20was%20thwarted%20by%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20around%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20associates%20contradicted%20official%20statements%20that%20the%20death%20was%20investigated%20by%20West%20Midlands%20police.%20The%20police%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20take%20statements%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20after%20his%20death%2C%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20his%20employers%20or%20work%20colleagues%2C%20did%20not%20retrace%20his%20steps%20on%20the%20days%20before%20his%20sudden%20illness%2C%20did%20not%20visit%20his%20residence%20or%20study%20threats%20made%20against%20him%2C%20and%20did%20not%20issue%20a%20case%20number%2C%20which%20would%20indicate%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20investigated%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20Khanda%20appeared%20%E2%80%9Chealthy%20and%20robust%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20weeks%20before%20his%20death%2C%20associates%20in%20Birmingham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%20and%20sister%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20they%20were%20the%20subject%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Caggressive%20intimidation%20campaign%20by%20Indian%20authorities%20in%20the%20months%20before%20%5BKhanda%E2%80%99s%5D%20death%E2%80%9D.%20While%20Indian%20agencies%20considered%20Khanda%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Amritpal%20Singh%2C%20the%20Sikh%20separatist%20and%20leader%20of%20Waris%20Punjab%20De%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famritpal-surrenders-himself-to-punjab-police-to-be-shifted-to-assam-soon%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%20in%20April%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20family%20%E2%80%9Cstaunchly%E2%80%9D%20denied%20any%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Amritpal%20Singh%20was%20on%20the%20run%2C%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20mother%20and%20sister%20were%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fpunjab%2Fuk-based-activist-khandas-mother-among-3-detained-496763%5C%22%3Epicked%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20by%20the%20Punjab%20police.%20His%20sister%20Jaspreet%20Kaur%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20at%20the%20police%20station%2C%20the%20police%20used%20her%20phone%20to%20call%20Khanda%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20instructed%20her%20%E2%80%9Cto%20tell%20my%20brother%20that%20I%20was%20on%20my%20own%20and%20ask%20him%20to%20confide%20in%20me%3A%20that%20the%20police%20were%20harassing%20me%20but%20I%20had%20found%20a%20room%20to%20myself%20and%20could%20he%20tell%20me%20where%20is%20Amritpal%20Singh%20hiding%20and%20can%20he%20give%20any%20details%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20questioning%20they%20would%20call%20Avtar%20from%20my%20phone%20and%20speak%20directly%20to%20him%2C%20making%20threats%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%98we%E2%80%99ve%20got%20your%20sister%20here%2C%20where%20is%20Amritpal%3F%20We%20know%20that%20you%20know.%E2%80%99%20Avtar%E2%80%99s%20response%20would%20always%20be%20the%20same%3A%20that%20he%20had%20never%20met%20Amritpal%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20where%20he%20was%20and%20could%20the%20police%20please%20stop%20harassing%20his%20family%20who%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20this%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20they%20or%20I%20can%20give%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhanda%2C%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20his%20personal%20Facebook%20page%20in%20April%2C%20also%20complained%20about%20the%20Indian%20police%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20harassment%20of%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20have%20been%20harassing%20me%20for%20the%20last%20four%20days.%20I%20am%20getting%20calls%20after%20calls%20from%20different%20police%20stations%20and%20they%20say%20the%20same%20thing%20again%20and%20again%20and%20again%2C%20and%20that%20is%20%E2%80%98where%20is%20Amritpal%20Singh%3F%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20Polak%2C%20a%20lawyer%20representing%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20said%20the%20activist%20%E2%80%9Cbegan%20receiving%20threats%20against%20his%20life%E2%80%9D%20after%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cwrongly%20implicated%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20Indian%20flag%20from%20the%20high%20commission%20of%20Indian%20in%20London%20in%20March%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701767126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05140946%2Fkhanda.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findian-police-harass-sikh-activist-avtar-singh-khanda-sudden-death-the-guardian%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20newspaper's%20investigation%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20UK%20police's%20earlier%20claim%20that%20Avtar%20Singh%20Khanda's%20death%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bthorough%20review%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20foul%20play%20suspected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findian-police-harass-sikh-activist-avtar-singh-khanda-sudden-death-the-guardian%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zoya%20wants%20to%20work%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20but..%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701767079000%2