ister%20-%20have%20made%20the%20same%20mistake.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fhs3vet9o_telangana-rural-seats-table-ndtv_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Urban%20-%20Rural%20divide%20gets%20starker%20when%20you%20see%20the%20results%20in%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20region.%20Of%20the%2024%20seats%2C%20the%20BRS%20won%2016.%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20%C2%A0All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Musalmeen%20(AIMIM)%20had%20its%20stranglehold%20over%20seven%20seats%20in%20Hyderabad.%20The%20BJP%20could%20win%20only%20one%20seat%20and%20the%20Congress%20was%20routed.%20The%20Congress%20had%20won%20two%20seats%20in%202018%20and%20both%20the%20winners%20shifted%20to%20the%20BRS.%20They%20won%20as%20BRS%20candidates%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20eight%20urban%20seats%20outside%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20region%2C%20the%20Congress%20gained%20three%20seats%20and%20the%20BRS%20lost%20three.%20This%20may%20suggest%20that%20the%20more%20one%20moves%20out%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20weaker%20the%20BRS%20becomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Feep5ug68_telangana-urban-seats-table-ndtv_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F1qr28gag_telangana-greater-hyderabad-seats-table-ndtv_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20can%20be%20broadly%20di