0%9Cphysiological%20limitations%E2%80%9D%20as%20being%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Csex%20stereotypes%E2%80%9D%20and%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Cgender%20discrimination%20against%20women%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Hindustan%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20said%20that%20all%20women%20Short%20Service%20Commission%20(SSC)%20had%20to%20be%20considered%20for%20permanent%20commission%20irrespective%20of%20them%20having%20completed%2014%20years%20or%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%2C%2020%20years%20of%20service%20within%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20after%20that%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20the%20Navy%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20It%20had%20said%20that%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20would%20ensure%20women%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20overcome%20%E2%80%9Chistories%20of%20discrimination%E2%80%9D%20in%20its%20March%2C%202020%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAG%20Venkatramani%20told%20the%20court%20that%20an%20officer%20must%20meet%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fform-policy-on-women-officers-promotion-sc-101701715027671.html%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cessential%20eligibility%20criteria%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20minimum%202%20confidential%20reports%20in%20Colonel%20Select%20rank.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20deviation%20from%20this%20fundamental%20eligibility%20criteria%20will%20amount%20to%20compromising%20with%20the%20operational%20requirement%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20to%20earn%20the%20rank%20of%20brigadier%2C%20an%20Army%20officer%20is%20required%20to%20experience%20operational%20command%20of%20a%20unit%20or%20battalion%20for%20a%20period%20of%20nearly%202%20years.%20This%20experience%20and%20service%20knowledge%20as%20commanding%20officer%20of%20a%20unit%20helps%20officers%20to%20understand%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintricacies%2C%20nuances%20and%20complexities%E2%80%9D%20of%20command%2C%20Venkataramani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicant%20officers%2C%20represented%20by%20advocate%20Archana%20Pathak%20Dave%2C%20informed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fform-policy-on-women-officers-promotion-sc-101701715027671.html%5C%22%3Ewomen%20have%20fought%20a%20long%20drawn%20battle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20courts%20to%20get%20their%20due.%20They%20said%20that%20command%20roles%20were%20made%20available%20to%20women%20only%20after%20the%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%202020%20decision%20on%20considering%20SSC%20women%20officers%20for%20PC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202021%2C%20the%20court%20found%20that%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20yardstick%20to%20grant%20PC%20to%20women%20officers%20was%20discriminatory%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20criteria%20for%20male%20officers.%20Dave%20said%20that%20the%20applicants%20only%20seek%20a%20policy%20to%20be%20put%20in%20place%20for%20governing%20promotions%20by%20special%20board%203%20(SB-3)%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fform-policy-on-women-officers-promotion-sc-101701715027671.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AG%20countered%20this%20by%20saying%20that%20all%20Army%20policies%20are%20%E2%80%9Cgender-neutral%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20applicants%20should%20not%20push%20the%20matter%20beyond%20a%20certain%20point.%20He%20said%20most%20of%20the%20women%20officers%20before%20the%20court%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20eligibility%20criteria%20for%20brigadier%20with%20command%20positions%20given%20to%20them%20after%20June%20this%20year%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20all%20because%20we%20pushed%20the%20envelope.%20We%20nudged%20you%2C%20otherwise%20nothing%20would%20have%20happened.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Court%20told%20Venkataramani%20that%20the%20Army%20had%20shown%20resistance%20by%20citing%20operational%20efficiency%20as%20a%20ground%20to%20justify%20denial%20of%20permanent%20commission%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20your%20case%20that%20operational%20preparedness%20of%20Army%20has%20been%20affected%20in%20any%20manner%20with%20women%20coming%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20submitted%20to%20Court%2C%20the%20AG%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20experience%20of%20performing%20in%20colonel%E2%80%99s%20rank%20is%20utmost%20essential%20to%20gauge%20any%20officer%E2%80%99s%20fitness%20for%20higher%20appointment.%20Any%20exception%20to%20this%20will%20have%20ramifications%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20leadership%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20along%20with%20opening%20avenues%20for%20many%20others%20who%20are%20deficient%20of%20command%20criteria%20to%20seek%20similar%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-pulls-up-army-for-denying-promotion-to-women-pc-officers-101699022243953.html%5C%22%3Etop%20court%20had%20criticised%20the%20Army%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20denying%20promotions%20to%20women%20permanent%20commission%20officers%20in%20November%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-pulls-up-army-for-denying-promotion-to-women-pc-officers-101699022243953.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20attitude%20has%20been%20to%20find%20some%20way%20to%20defeat%20the%20just%20entitlements%20of%20women%20officers.%20Such%20an%20approach%20does%20disservice%20to%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20justice%20to%20the%20women%20officers%2C%20who%20have%20already%20fought%20a%20long%20and%20hard%20battle%2C%20to%20get%20their%20just%20entitlements%20under%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20officers%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20last%20year%20as%20SB-3%20that%20empanels%20officers%20as%20colonel%20had%20not%20met%20for%2018%20months%20despite%20the%2