%2Fa%3E%20reports%20that%20four%20others%20with%20the%20same%20name%20figure%20in%20the%20registry.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20all%20under%20trial%20in%20other%20states%2C%20not%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20inquired%20about%20the%20person%20named%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20and%20the%20prima%20facie%20inquiry%20did%20not%20find%20any%20case%20against%20him%20after%20I%20confirmed%20with%20all%20the%20four%20commissionerates%20in%20Gujarat.%20All%20the%20DCPs%20(district%20commissioners%20of%20police)%20from%20the%20city%20confirmed%20that%20they%20did%20not%20know%20who%20Gupta%20was%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20director%20general%20of%20police%20Vikas%20Sahay%20told%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20federal%20prosecutors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3Ehave%20filed%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cmurder%20for%20hire%E2%80%9D%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Indian%20national%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20%E2%80%93%20a%20resident%20of%20India%20who%20had%20been%20the%20cutout%2C%20or%20go-between%2C%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20used%20to%20hire%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%20associate%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%E2%80%98criminal%20associate%E2%80%99%20in%20turn%20introduced%20Gupta%20to%20a%20hitman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%20for%20Gupta%20and%20his%20alleged%20handlers%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98criminal%20associate%E2%80%99%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconfidential%20source%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20US%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Agency%20while%20the%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%20he%20connected%20Gupta%20to%20was%20an%20undercover%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20also%20contains%20damaging%20information%20about%20the%20unnamed%20Indian%20official%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20June%2018%2C%202023%20assassination%20of%20Khalistani%20activist%20Hardeep%20Nijjar%20in%20Canada%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20ad