artland%20states%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20The%20BJP%20knows%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20stop%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20from%20making%20any%20headway%20in%202024%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20seats%20confined%C2%A0%20to%20a%20double-digit%20figure%2C%20overall.%20The%20Congress%20knows%20it%20has%20to%20cross%20the%20100-seat%20mark%2C%20up%20from%2052%20last%20time%2C%20to%20create%20a%20small%20chance%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20to%20make%20a%20bid%20for%20power%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20are%20crucial%20to%20this%20Opposition%20project%20because%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20have%20a%20straight%20fight%20here.%20The%20INDIA%20alliance%20had%20hoped%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%C2%A0%20improve%20in%20these%20states%20from%20an%20abysmally%20low%20base.%20In%20MP%2C%20with%2029%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20got%20just%20one%20in%202019%20and%20the%20BJP%20swept%2028.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20Congress%20got%20zero%20and%20the%20BJP%20bagged%2024%20out%20of%2025%20seats.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20get%20just%20two%20seats%20out%20of%2011%20and%20the%20BJP%20got%20the%20remaining%20nine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strike%20rate%20in%20these%20three%20states%20was%20close%20to%20100%25%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20There%20was%20some%20rational%20expectation%20that%20the%20Congress%20could%20do%20better%20from%20such%20a%20low%20base.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20was%20always%20assumed%20that%2010%20years%20of%20anti-incumbency%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20cause%20the%20BJP%20to%20cede%20at%20least%2030-40%25%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20three%20states.%20It%20is%20not%20an%20unreasonable%20hypothesis%20that%20the%20BJP%20still%20retains%2060%25%20of%20the%20seats%20on%20the%20back%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20assembly%20election%20results%20should%20provoke%20a%20rethink%20in%20the%20Congress%20camp.%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decisive%20win%20has%20created%20a%20groundswell%20of%20positive%20sentiment%20for%20Modi%20just%20six%20months%20ahead%20of%20general%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20could%20still%20retain%20100%25%20of%20the%20seats%20if%20the%20Congress%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20gear%20up%20to%20fight%20the%20battle%20of%20its%20lifetime%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Myth%20of%20BJP's%20Hat-Trick%20and%20What%20the%20Statistics%20Really%20Say%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-assembly-elections-hat-trick-2024%5C%22%3EThe%20Myth%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hat-Trick%20and%20What%20the%20Statistics%20Really%20Say%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20silver%20lining%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20have%20retained%20its%20vote%20share%20(improved%20by%200.5%25%20in%20Rajasthan)%20in%20these%20states%20compared%20to%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20it%20won%20a%20majority%20in%20all%20three.%20Even%20if%20the%20Congress%20is%20able%20to%20retain%20this%20vote%20share%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20it%20may%20have%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20winning%20over%2020%20seats%20from%20the%20three%20states.%20But%20this%20may%20not%20be%20easy%2C%20as%20the%20Modi%20factor%20will%20be%20stronger%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20The%20vote%20share%20gap%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20was%C2%A0%20huge.%20In%20Rajasthan%20and%20MP%2C%20the%20BJP%20got%2058-60%25%20of%20votes%20whereas%20the%20Congress%20was%20stuck%20at%2034%25.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20BJP%20got%2050%25%20of%20the%20votes%20and%20Congress%2040%25.%20The%20BJP%20has%20a%20huge%20lead%20over%20the%20Congress%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20OBCs.%20The%20yawning%20vote%20share%20gap%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20is%20largely%20explained%20by%20the%20OBC%20vote%2C%20over%20which%20Modi%20has%20particular%20sway.%20Also%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20with%20its%20new%20focus%20on%20caste%20census%20politics%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20given%20up%20on%20the%20upper%20caste%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20caste%20census%20politics%2C%20on%20which%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20banking%2C%20help%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20apart%20from%20Bihar%3F%20Though%20the%20Congress%20has%20a%20fairly%20impressive%20share%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20votes%20in%20state%20elections%2C%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20much%20of%20this%20might%20shift%20to%20Modi%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20However%2C%20the%20OBC%20consolidation%20behind%20Modi%20is%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room.%20A%20key%20question%20here%20again%20is%20how%20much%20the%20caste%20census%20will%20work%20in%20the%20cow%20belt%20states%20outside%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20how%20will%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20create%20proper%20messaging%20of%20its%20vision%20of%20how%20Mandal%202.0%20would%20play%20out%2C%20based%20on%20a%20new%20national%20caste%20census%3F%20This%20is%20a%20very%20important%20question%20that%20will%20determine%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%2C%20where%20it%20is%20in%20a%20one-to-one%20fight%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Recently%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Sushil%20Modi%2C%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20argued%20that%20Modi%20is%20already%20doing%20enough%20for%20the%20OBC%20community%20and%20need%20not%20depend%20on%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20prove%20his%20credentials.%20There%20may%20be%20some%20truth%20in%20this%2C%20at%20least%20outside%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Behind%20Congress%20Defeat%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20Clear%20Rejection%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20Leadership%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbehind-congress-defeat-madhya-pradesh-kamal-nath-rejection%5C%22%3EBehind%20Congress%20Defeat%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20Clear%20Rejection%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20Leadership%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20MP%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20caste%20census%20politics%20did%20not%20resonate%20much%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20Paradoxically%2C%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20be%20expanding%20its%20OBC%20vote%20bank%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20without%20depending%20much%20on%20the%20caste%20census%20pitch.%20Its%20win%20in%20Telangana%20is%20backed%20by%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20the%20OBC%20vote%20shifting%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi.%20Traditionally%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20dominated%20by%20the%20upper%20caste%20Reddy%20community%20but%20now%20is%20also%20backed%20by%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20Muslims.%20This%20was%20the%20old%20caste%20coalition%20which%20the%20Congress%20enjoyed%20under%20Indira%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20by%20and%20large%20may%20not%20even%20need%20an%20aggressive%20caste%20census%20pitch%20as%20a%20realpolitik%20tool%20because%20the%20politics%20of%20social%20empowerment%20in%20many%20of%20these%20states%20has%20deep%20roots.%20In%20contrast%2C%20backward%20caste%20empowerment%20politics%20in%20the%20North%20is%20of%20more%20recent%20origin%2C%20post%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20report.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20counter%20to%20Mandal%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20consolidation%2C%20has%20weaned%20away%20large%20sections%20of%20OBCs%20in%20the%20broader%20Hindi-speaking%20belt.%20Remember%2C%20the%20Sangh%20had%20consciously%20involved%20the%20OBC%20community%20in%20the%20aggressive%20campaign%20for%20Ram%20Mandir%20to%20counter%20the%20Mandal%20mobilisation.%20Large%20sections%20of%20the%20OBC%20community%20in%20the%20North%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20transactional%20nexus%20with%20political%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20challenge%20is%20to%20penetrate%20the%20OBC%20vote%20in%20this%20region.%20Will%20caste%20census%20politics%20enable%20this%3F%20If%20not%2C%20what%20alternative%20vision%20will%20INDIA%20present%3F%20This%20has%20to%20be%20decided%C2%A0%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701753726000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29081646%2FGABI58kWMAANlJC.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-has-no-option-but-to-recover-in-heartland-states-in-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20are%20crucial%20to%20this%20Opposition%20project%20because%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20have%20a%20straight%20fight%20here.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-has-no-option-but-to-recover-in-heartland-states-in-2024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forest%20City%3A%20Inside%20Malaysia's%20Chinese-built%20'ghost%20city'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701753608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17FC2%2Fproduction%2F_131924289_gettyimages-1636808565.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67610677%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Built%20during%20the%20Chinese%20property%20boom%2C%20Forest%20City%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20crisis%20in%20the%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A312%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67610677%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67610677.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67610677.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nepal%20urges%20Russia%20not%20to%20recruit%20its%20citizens%20into%20army%3B%20sa