nt-parliament-9054207%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Higher%20Education%20sector%20students%20have%20multiple%20options%20and%20they%20choose%20to%20migrate%20across%20institutions%20and%20from%20one%20course%2Fprogramme%20to%20another%20in%20the%20same%20institution.%20The%20migration%2Fwithdrawal%20if%20any%2C%20is%20mainly%20on%20account%20of%20securing%20seat%20by%20the%20students%20in%20other%20departments%20or%20institutions%20of%20their%20choice%20or%20on%20any%20personal%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20gave%20a%20breakup%20of%20the%20students%20who%20have%20dropped%20out%20of%20various%20institutions.%20Around%204%2C596%20OBC%20candidates%2C%202%2C424%20SC%20and%202%2C622%20ST%20students%20dropped%20out%20of%20central%20universities%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20While%20as%20many%20as%202%2C066%20OBC%20candidates%2C%201%2C068%20SC%20and%20408%20ST%20students%20dropped%20out%20of%20IITs%20and%20163%20OBC%2C%20188%20SC%20and%2091%20ST%20candidates%20dropped%20out%20of%20IIMs%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Feducation%2Fover-13000-sc-st-and-obc-students-dropped-out-of-central-varsities-iits-iims-in-5-years-minister-of-state-for-education-government-parliament-9054207%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20proactively%20address%20any%20issues%20of%20SC%2FST%20students%2C%20institutes%20have%20set%20up%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20SC%2FST%20students%E2%80%99%20cells%2C%20Equal%20Opportunity%20Cell%2C%20Student%20Grievance%20Cell%2C%20Student%20Grievance%20Committee%2C%20Students%20Social%20Club%2C%20Liaison%20officers%2C%20Liaison%20Committee%20etc.%20Further%2C%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20has%20issued%20instructions%20from%20time%20to%20time%20for%20promoting%20equity%20and%20fraternity%20amongst%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5